            {
              "rowId": 15,
              "keyParts": [
                15,
                "p2",
                "verse",
                "v2",
                "label"
              ],
              "value": "2"
            },
            {
              "rowId": 16,
              "keyParts": [
                16,
                "p2",
                "verse",
                "v2",
                "content"
              ],
              "value": "He created them male and female; when they were created, he blessed them and named them “humankind.”"
            },
            {
              "rowId": 17,
              "keyParts": [
                17,
                "p2",
                "verse",
                "v2",
                "note",
                "f"
              ],
              "value": "tn The Hebrew word used here is אָדָם (’adam)."
            },
            {
